rows.label: qst701105_msg0001
rows.name:
...You're looking for a skipper?
And you're serious about it?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, but my services don't come cheap,
darlings. Let's see now... My rates are...
Hmm. How's 200,000G sound?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0101
rows.name: What will you do?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0102
rows.name: Turn her down

rows.label: qst701105_msg0103
rows.name: Pay up

rows.label: qst701105_msg0104
rows.name: Mention Arb's name

rows.label: qst701105_msg0201
rows.name:
Nooo! For reals?
Aww, well, come again, darlings. ♪

rows.label: qst701105_msg0301
rows.name:
Urk-! You've seriously got that kind
of scratch? What are you, highborn
or something?!

rows.label: qst701105_msg0302
rows.name:
No no, not a problem! Nope, I'm good.
I'll do it! Just tell me where to be and
I'll be there with bells on.

rows.label: qst701105_msg0303
rows.name:
...Yanchik Harbor? Yep, got it.
By the by, d'you need me to go in all
sneaky-like? Is someone after you?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0304
rows.name:
...Oh, you're not really involved? Still,
your pockets have got to be quite deep,
throwing money around like that...

rows.label: qst701105_msg0305
rows.name:
Huh? Oh, don't mind me, darlings.
Let's just meet in Yanchik Harbor.
Toodle-pip, and all that. ♪

rows.label: qst701105_msg0401
rows.name:
Oh, you're friends with the old fart?
Well, why didn't you say so sooner,
darlings?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0402
rows.name:
If you need a skipper, I'll be there.
I can't very well refuse if he's asking...
I'm sure he's got reasons to, and so on.

rows.label: qst701105_msg0403
rows.name:
...What, money? Nah, forget about it!
I'm not so far gone that I can't do a
friend a favor. So, where do I go?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0404
rows.name:
...Yanchik Harbor? Yep, got it.
By the by, d'you need me to go in all
sneaky-like? Is someone after you?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0405
rows.name:
...Oh, you're not really involved?
Cool. No precautions necessary, then.

rows.label: qst701105_msg0406
rows.name:
Huh? Oh, don't mind me, darlings.
Let's just meet in Yanchik Harbor.
Toodle-pip, and all that. ♪

rows.label: qst701105_msg0501
rows.name: Will you pay 200,000G?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0502
rows.name: Don't pay

rows.label: qst701105_msg0503
rows.name: Aww pooh, so you're short after all...
